<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rgẖm ạlḍyqẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rgẖm ạlḍyqẗ wrgẖm ạljrḥ sạmʿ ṣwtk jwh fy qlby
 wạ̉nạ tʿbạn mḥrwm m ạlfrḥ ʿạrfk dạymaⁿạ wạqf jnby
 ạlqrạr- ʿyny ʿlyk mstny tʿwd tmly̱ bnwrk qlby ạlmṭfy
 ạqfl jrḥy wḥṭ wrwd ạrfʿny dạ ạ̉nạ mạyl mkfy
 2- ạsndny wạdyny slạm kẖly ạlḥzn fy rwḥy ynạm
 wạlklmẗ tqwyny fy ḍʿfy wthwn ly ạlạ̉yạm
 3- lm ạlsẖwk mn zrʿ ạlʿạlm yạlly bḥạl ạ̉wlạdk ʿạlm
 lyk slṭạn ʿ ạlsẖr yạ rby mạ ạ̹nt ạ̉bwyạ wfy qlbk nạym</lyrics>
